
Project Outline
- Features
    - Add Folder(s) 
        - folder tile change to dynamic - user imput (done)
    - Edit Folders (s) (done)
    - Remove Folder(s) - (done)
    - Identify which folder the items are being add/edit/etc to.(done)
    - Add new items to folder (done)
    - Remove items within folder (done)
    - List items within folder (done)
    - Edit items within folder (done)
    - Search for item in folder (done)
    - Search for item using Title (done)
    
   
